source:
TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_SEQ_00Uin Nee has a need for nectar.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe
Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe ou le job qui a servi à la commencer.

Uin Nee semble avoir un petit problème de nectar.

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_TODO_01<tab>Ride the porxie to Handmirror Lake and suck up some nectar.
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_TODO_01<tab>À dos de porxie, utiliser “Inspiration” sur des fleurs épanouies près du lac Beaumiroir
TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_TODO_02<tab>Parler à Uin Nee, à Lydha Lran

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_000<tab>Shall we play a guessing game, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>? Guess what I love more than <var 1A 02 /var>anything<var 1A 01 /var> in the world! No, it's not you, silly. It's nectar! Sweet, luscious, lovely nectar!
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_000<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, tu dois sûrement savoir que nous autres Pixies adoooorons le nectar<var 1D /var>? Plus il est sucré, mieux c'est. On en consomme des tonz, et on a même une réserve stratégique pour parer à toute pénurie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_001<tab>And guess what I love <var 1A 02 /var>almost<var 1A 01 /var> as much as nectar? Why, the simply <var 1A 02 /var>perfect<var 1A 01 /var> porxies the Nu Mou made for us to gather all the nectar we can drink!
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_001<tab>Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, elle a été cambriolée par un gang de Nu Mousard contrebandiers, et il y a beaucoup de travail pour la remplir à nouveau<var 1D /var>! Tu veux bien nous donner un coup de main<var 1D /var>? Tu vas voir, c'est très amusant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_002<tab>Now let <var 1A 02 /var>me<var 1A 01 /var> guess: you've always wanted to ride a porxie, too? Well, then today's your lucky day! Simply speak to my friend Lugg Aenc, and they'll have you on the back of one of our fetching little familiars in no time! Doesn't that sound like fun?
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_002<tab>Il suffit que tu parles à Lugg Aenc pour chevaucher un de ses porxies, et il t'expliquera tout ce que tu dois savoir. Je compte sur toi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_LUGGAENC_000_010<tab>Greetings, friend! Do not worry─Uin Nee has already explained everything to me. You'll be taking one of our porxies out to harvest a healthy supply of nectar, correct? It really is too kind of you to volunteer for such a tedious task. In any event, I'm happy to afford you with one of my personal favorites.
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_LUGGAENC_000_010<tab>Ah, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var><var 1D /var>! Je vous attendais. Pour récolter du nectar, montez sur un de mes porxies, rendez-vous près du lac Beaumiroir et faites-le inspirer près de fleurs épanouies. Retournez voir Uin Nee quand vous aurez terminé<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_LUGGAENC_000_011<tab>Are you quite all right? When the porxie returned alone, I'd worried that you'd taken a nasty fall. Good to see that you're still up and about─Uin Nee's getting terribly impatient about that nectar you promised them.
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_LUGGAENC_000_011<tab>Quand j'ai vu mon porxie revenir sans vous, je savais bien qu'il s'était passé quelque chose... Tout va bien<var 1D /var>? Si vous êtes <var 08 E905 ((prête)) ((prêt)) /var> à repartir, voilà une autre monture pour vous<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_SYSTEM_000_012<tab>The porxie inhales deeply, filling its nose─and one can only assume other parts of its inner anatomy─with sweet, sweet nectar. You try not to think about how Uin Nee intends to extract said nectar from the innards of the little beast.
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_SYSTEM_000_012<tab>Le porxie a aspiré tout le nectar de cette fleur<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_SYSTEM_000_013<tab>The aroma of sweet nectar wafts toward your nose. Unfortunately, you have no way of harvesting it on your own. Speak to Lugg Aenc in Lydha Lran so that you might procure a porxie and remedy the situation.
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_SYSTEM_000_013<tab>Cette fleur semble contenir une grande quantité de nectar sucré. Parlez à Lugg Aenc, à Lydha Lran, pour chevaucher un porxie puis utilisez “Inspiration” pour aspirer le nectar.

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_020<tab>Oh, hello there. A porxie just came back with a belly full of the sweetest, most succulent nectar. I don't suppose you had anything to do with that, did you? In any event, I do hope you enjoyed your little flight!
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_020<tab>Je viens d'apercevoir ton porxie, il avait le ventre rond comme un ballon<var 1D /var>! Merci pour tout ce délicieux nectar que tu nous a apporté. Avec ça, notre réserve stratégique a meilleure mine, hi hi<var 1D /var>!♪

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_021<tab>Yes, I simply can't wait to drink deep of that sweet, sweet nectar! Oh, perhaps you were wondering how we get the nectar out of the porxie?
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_021<tab>Pour te remercier de ton aide, je vais te confier un petit secret. Tu sais qu'on appelle “miel” le nectar récolté par les abeilles, n'est-ce pas<var 1D /var>? À ton avis, comment on appelle celui des porxies<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_022<tab>Well, if you must know...I try not to think about that part. It gets a bit icky from time to time, you see. Why, there was one time when a porxie sneezed just as I was about to─yuck! On second thought, I don't think I'm thirsty anymore. Oh, why did you have to remind me about that!?
target: TEXT_BANPIX110_03698_UINNEE_000_022<tab>... Le <var 1A 02 /var>cochoniel<var 1A 01 /var><var 1D /var>! Tu saisis<var 1D /var>? Porxie, cochon, miel... cochoniel<var 1D /var>! Comment ça c'est pas drôle<var 1D /var>? Bah, on s'en moque tant que c'est super mignon, hi hi<var 1D /var>!♪
